{"tid":2322790,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–流感疫苗的重要發展","createTime":"2020-12-12T15:13:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T17:52:24.000Z","uid":38861,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"bdf19f7e8c79e7cbf0ceab59d5f0487004229876","tid":2322790,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T15:13:20.000Z","msg":"季節性流感造成全球每年約290,000-650,000人的死亡。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Xs2hxP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Xs2hxP.jpg&h=525e6326&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n流感病毒接近每年均會出現變種，基於現時並無統一疫苗對抗各品種，所以很多時候在翌年便要轉換對應的疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n(圖2)流感病毒外部、名為HA的部份，將主宰病毒能否進入人體細胞裡頭。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/miRZjMd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmiRZjMd.png&h=6d8a0c99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n流感病毒的變異較常出現在頭部位置(Head)，而現時疫苗的設計亦主要針對HA的頭部位置。<br />\n<br />\n其目標是希望人們注射疫苗後，體內會產生對應HA頭部位置的抗體，阻止病毒進入人體細胞繼而作惡。<br />\n<br />\n(圖3)另一方面來想，流感病毒變種就如不同顏色的花朵一樣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dgmnhxY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdgmnhxY.png&h=b9af7d8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然花朵各有不同，但莖部位置則大同小異。<br />\n<br />\n(圖4)基於Stalk位置(花朵莖部位置)的變異成數較細，現時科學家正研發針對Stalk位置的疫苗(Ref1)，希望可以透過一款疫苗對抗多款流感變種。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dXDdpdm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdXDdpdm.png&h=819bd187&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這類型的疫苗現時已進入Phase1狀態，人體試驗找來了51名人士，注射疫苗後體內亦得出相應的大量抗體。<br />\n<br />\n而日後所進行的人體試驗，將會能夠獲取資料測量疫苗能否達到預防流感之效。<br />\n<br />\n若安全性、效率等等均達到合理水平的話，將來不但之可以不用經常轉換疫苗款式，亦能大大減低疫苗與當下流感款式不吻合的機會，皆大歡喜。<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"teal\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"red\">like</span>以及<span class=\"blue\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jciEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=b8aae5cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jciEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=fcaea4b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fpotatopigtongue%2F&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jciEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=1ee5ea98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41591-020-1118-7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41591-020-1118-7&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jciEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=af286a98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s41591-020-1118-7</a>"},{"pid":"7078ae10ec52ff098a61ad9299e1ec2e6cd07546","tid":2322790,"uid":380296,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T15:13:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a27aa9ff245e0b51f7c80e687b555c056a5510db","tid":232